{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_09_01",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらくした頃",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 2.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日もお疲れ様。生放送にインタビュー、CM撮影\nまであって大忙しだったな。体調は大丈夫か？",
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。むしろ{user}さんこそ\n疲れた顔されてませんか？",
      "startTime": 14.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "う、鋭いな。今度の打ち合わせ用に資料を作っていたら\nつい熱が入って……気付けば日付が変わっていてな",
      "startTime": 22.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私達のために、遅くまでありがとうございます\nでも、たまには自分の体も労わって下さいね",
      "startTime": 31.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。もうすぐ新曲のMV撮影もあるし\nお互い体調には気をつけていこう",
      "startTime": 39.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だが、これだけ過密なスケジュールなのに\n沙季は普段とまるで変わらないな。本当に凄いよ",
      "startTime": 45.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私の場合、千紗の忙しさをそばで見ていたのが\n大きいですね。その分、覚悟は出来ていましたから",
      "startTime": 53.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、睡眠や食事は必ず十分に取ること\nそれ以外のことも表にまとめて、焦らず行動すること",
      "startTime": 63.9000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが組んだスケジュールに\n無理はないはずですし、一つ一つこなせば大丈夫です",
      "startTime": 69.8944863583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "もし体調を崩してしまう子がいたら、出来る限り\nフォローしますから、いつでも頼って下さいね",
      "startTime": 77.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗を間近で見ていたからこそ、ってことか\n沙季みたいに冷静な子がいると、周りも安心出来そうだ",
      "startTime": 85.1666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ。アイドルとしてお仕事を沢山いただけるのは\n嬉しいですし、みんなで乗り切っていきたいですね",
      "startTime": 93.1227160057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、忙しいのはありがたいんですが……最近はお断り\nしている仕事が増えてしまってるのが心苦しいですね",
      "startTime": 102.4333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "沙季の時間や体力にも限界があるからな。なるべく多く\n受けられるよう調整しているんだが、申し訳ない",
      "startTime": 111.2204013955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ希望は尊重したいと思ってるから、優先したい\n仕事や、やってみたい仕事があったら教えてくれ",
      "startTime": 118.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "優先したい仕事……そうですね、そういう意味では\nレギュラー出演している番組を、何より優先したいです",
      "startTime": 129.0333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "これまでいただいたお仕事があったからこそ\n今の私がありますから。しっかりとご恩に報いたいです",
      "startTime": 136.2000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、新しいお仕事の話も聞いてみたいですね\n指名してもらうからには、出来る限り頑張りたいです",
      "startTime": 145.9333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "その上で、希望があるとすれば……自分の趣味を\n生かせるようなお仕事に挑戦してみたいです",
      "startTime": 156.6666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "実は、千紗がホラーやファッション関係のお仕事を\nしてるのがちょっとだけ羨ましくて",
      "startTime": 163.2333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "そのためなら、今より多少忙しくなっても頑張ります\nまだ体力には余裕もありますし",
      "startTime": 171.4666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな\nよし、それじゃあ今度の打ち合わせで話してみるよ",
      "startTime": 176.1666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.1166713317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.1166713317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.2333335876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、始まりました！\n『街中探検・ぐるっとスタンプラリー』のお時間です！",
      "startTime": 184.2333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.1000046651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "今日は私、白石沙季と一緒に、スタンプラリーを\n通してこの街のことをより深く知っていきましょう！",
      "startTime": 191.6333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（さすがに自分から提案した企画だけに）\n（凄い熱の入りようだ）\n（局との打ち合わせに）\n（企画書持参で逆提案したんだもんな）",
      "startTime": 202.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.9666713317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、ここが一つ目のスタンプを押せる場所ですね\n現地の方にこの土地ゆかりのお話をうかがいましょう",
      "startTime": 210.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.8333400329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ、なるほど……あ！\nその戦国武将の方はよく知っています",
      "startTime": 220.7000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "戦場だけでなく、領内の治水事業でも腕を振るった文武\n両道な方ですよね。本を読んでいて胸が躍りました！",
      "startTime": 228.9333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233.9333400329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "え？　その話はちょうどこれから話そうとしていた？\nご、ごめんなさい！　失礼しました！",
      "startTime": 238.8728852689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（熱心さが裏目に出てしまったか……）\n（まぁ、これくらいのミスはご愛敬だよな）",
      "startTime": 246.1666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 250.4000068664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……よし、これでオールアップか\n沙季、撮影お疲れ様。ん……なんだ、そのぬいぐるみ？",
      "startTime": 254.5000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 260.7333318949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。これ、スタンプラリーのスタンプを\nコンプリートするともらえるんだそうです",
      "startTime": 264.8610326722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "戦国武将をモチーフにした『ぶしょこ』ってキャラです\n私この子が大好きで！　とっても可愛いですよね……！",
